    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[徐州逛吃]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/eating-in-xuzhou/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/eating-in-xuzhou/">
        </link>
        <updated>2025-07-23T04:59:08.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>虽然说是逛吃，其实都只是吃，只是临走的时候随便逛了逛云龙湖（并没有对掏）</p>
<p>刚下火车已经八点多了，一下午没吃饭已经挺饿了，去酒店的途中随便进了一家比较大的连锁烧烤店。<br>
一开始没反应过来，摆在了远离碳火的上层，烤了半天都没怎么熟，吃了两串才反应过来。<br>
只加了盐的白串实在是太好吃了，空口吃好吃，蘸甜醋吃好吃，裹饼吃也好吃。<br>
而且饿了半天来吃，居然才花了八十多。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753247735163.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>吃完饭在酒店附近打卡了 徐州老味菜</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753247882074.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>第二天早上起来一醒就已经十点了，所以直接开吃。去了朋友推荐的苏宁广场附近，果然好吃的特别多。</p>
<p>第一次喝幸运咖，苹果冰美式，还可以，才六块。<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753247956087.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>二中老郑烤肉筋，四串肉串卷饼才12，而且巨好吃。<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248076573.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>正餐吃的是什一餐厅，因为去的早还有位置，出去的时候发现已经排了不短的队了，不愧是徐州的必吃榜餐厅，含金量是有的。<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248159299.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>胳膊长的蒜爆鱼才39<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248251295.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248257172.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>油爆鸭，也好吃<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248286632.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248291961.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>最后打卡了云龙湖<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248305657.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>在景区喝到了徐州本地奶茶 蜜城之恋，这款西红柿鸡蛋汤实际是菠萝和西瓜果茶<br>
<img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753248401783.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[济南散步]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/jinan-walking/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/jinan-walking/">
        </link>
        <updated>2025-07-23T01:22:39.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>没有计划地散步，吃了两顿。</p>
<p>到达济南的第一餐，吃了春水锅贴。<br>
锅贴好吃的，素锅贴里面有虾仁，问了店员没法买半份，所以只点了一个素锅贴。<br>
风味茄子，茄子土豆是油炸过的，甜口，不太习惯。<br>
（店里面有人抽烟）</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753243270281.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>吃完饭逛了趵突泉和大明湖。</p>
<p>趵突泉除了本体外，就是大公园和一些展览馆，好在门票价格便宜，好像济南的景点要么免费要么挺便宜的都。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753243476443.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753243831719.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753245968296.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753245983855.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753245993764.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246003958.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>在大明湖看到了夏雨荷和荷花。公园内有很多桥可以横跨湖，但是没有环湖步道有点遗憾，我比较喜欢绕湖散步。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246017216.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246024672.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246103450.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246169539.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246178004.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>被滑到有坑的“滑梯”，加了防护还是有孩子和大孩子上去跃跃欲试，很欢乐。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246137607.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>国民党守军临时指挥部旧址，不到一米八根本碰不到头。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246155994.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>济南的便利店，特色饮料</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="15"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246254794.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>无糖崂山可乐还挺好喝，比普通有糖版好喝</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="16"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753246264291.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>晚上吃的隋坡探店推荐的春江饭店，两个菜我都不喜欢。</p>
<p>爆三样，我想吃视频里的爆双脆的，记错了点了这个。一开始只觉得挺咸，可能适合下饭，后来做成盖浇饭也嫌咸的程度，可能不同地方口味差异吧。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="17"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753235512462.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>九转大肠，甜口的，类似红烧肉，但是这个烧焦了，有苦味，这个肯定是有问题的。而且我和视频里同一个月去的店里，视频里这份大肠78，我这份98。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="18"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753235632115.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>第二天去了济南动物园和山东博物馆。</p>
<p>济南动物园，感觉设计一般，一半都是需要二次付费的游乐园，好在票价也便宜。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="19"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753240978405.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="20"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753240960221.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="21"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241010866.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>站在桥上看鹅鸭园，我带的可乐掉到水里砸出的水花喷到黑天鹅身上。<br>
我：那鸭子的眼神好像在说，我早看你不是好人<br>
我朋友：那是黑天鹅...</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="22"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241036384.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="23"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241063476.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="24"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241047715.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>下雨天小熊猫被关在了室内馆，而且没开灯</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="25"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241365908.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="26"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241387671.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="27"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241404236.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>下午去了山东博物馆，比想象中有意思，连我这种不爱逛博物馆的都喜欢，那些古代衣物盔甲，在显示器上看到可能没那么精细，但是现场看真的有点震撼，难怪大家都想买大的显示效果好的电视和显示器</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="28"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241509246.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="29"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241524864.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="30"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241539354.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="31"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1753241557239.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[小小泰山，拿下]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/taishan-travel/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post/taishan-travel/">
        </link>
        <updated>2025-07-14T21:46:52.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是一篇泰山旅行流水账</p>
<p>旅行是从绿皮火车卧铺开始的，这是我第一次坐卧铺，可能也是最后一次坐卧铺，至少会尽量避免中铺（或者上铺）。我无法忘记我尝试了几次，最后像一只蛆一样蛄蛹进中铺的难堪，让我颜面尽失。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529779556.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529785327.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>脚让一让，花生瓜子小零食嘞，有需要的吗。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529800651.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>窗外的景色，即将到达泰山站。泰山站和泰安站离泰山都挺近，区别好像是泰山站只有绿皮车，泰安站是高铁站。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529808245.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>早餐：本来想去另一家，从火车站步行一公里多结果没开门，赶紧打车来这家，虽然也不太远。这个汤叫糁汤，好像是一种鸡蛋汤；右边这盘叫三代子，好像是某种牛杂，中间有牛肉汤冻，本来汤就咸，如果加了这个就咸得受不了了；还有一盘油条和素包。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529816555.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>红门游客中心，步行上山的游客从这里开始。这里并没有开始验票。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529825476.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>这里开始是石阶山路了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529831836.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>著名的二虫，也就是风月无边。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529839572.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>这个招牌，我一眼看成电水帽，想起电影《绿里奇迹》里面加泡了水的海绵的电刑帽。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529846581.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>路上遇到两只小猫，在景点发现一群人突然围在一起，很有可能是发现小猫了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529855400.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529860969.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>下面这两样是我吃过最难吃的东西，这碗面尤甚。这碗说是叫杂酱面，就是有一点汤的热挂面，加了点黄瓜丝，一些黄豆酱，自己搅合搅合，我爬了半天这么饿，只吃了半口就吃不下去了，这碗20。</p>
<p>没走两步路就看到卖烤肠的，烤肠倒是泰山统一价，10块钱三根，但是这家感觉只是刚解冻加热到将将能吃（也可能不能吃只是恰巧我没坏肚子），后来看到其他的烤肠摊子都是正常的爆开的。</p>
<p>最坑的是，这里没走两步就是中天门，由于通了公路和客车，所以中天门这里物价更低，两块钱冰矿泉水，还有蜜雪冰城和肯德基。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529869829.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529875040.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>到达中天门，到了这就算走了一半了，不过后面就更难了，不管是体力还是绝对难度。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529882224.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>在这吃了豆芽炒肉丝，38的菜，8块的米饭，虽然也不咋好吃，但比那碗面还是好太多了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="15"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529888579.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>这蜜雪冰城基本和山下一样价了吧，对于景区和山里，可以说很良心了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="16"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529896014.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>十八盘，具体有多少这样的台阶有多少段，不管是向下看还是向上看都让人恐高。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="17"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529902263.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="18"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529908647.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>一路上不少地方的台阶很窄，一只脚都放不下，上山都不太方便，如果下山估计更难受。幸好下山赶上了缆车不用再走一遍。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="19"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529919187.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>“森林防火 重于泰山” 不如直接压死我，都省得跳了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="20"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529926085.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>偶遇“好莱坞”（著名博客听众）</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="21"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529933119.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>到达南天门，快到终点最高点了。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="22"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529944593.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>到达玉皇顶，这应该是最高点了吧。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="23"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529953602.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="24"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529961026.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>缆车运营到下午五点半，还好赶上了，不用自己步行下山。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="25"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529969079.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>在路上又看见一个“好莱坞”，回看到时候才发现下面的清真猪头肉。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="26"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529976443.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>超英美容院，超英赶美学院。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="27"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529983317.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>全国连锁，仅此一家的绿豆饼，羡慕泰安人的精神状态。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="28"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529989150.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>晚餐，油条拌黄瓜，和我想象中的不一样，油条太脆了，酱汁又太浓郁，我还以为这道菜的油条类似新炸的油条或者只是老油条用空气炸锅之类再加热一下，酱我以为会更清爽些。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="29"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752529999671.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>泰安炒鸡，和别的山东炒鸡不一样，是先油炸再干炒的，好吃。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="30"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752530010543.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>冰淇淋烤布蕾，在别的店也吃过，不知道是不是预制的。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="31"><img src="https://blog.hellomawing.com/post-images/1752530017942.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
]]></content>
